&lt;h1&gt;


Made-in-China.com vs DHgate vs Yiwugo: Which Platform to Scrape for Wholesale Product Data
&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you're building tools for wholesale sourcing, price monitoring, or supplier discovery, you've probably wondered: &lt;strong&gt;which Chinese wholesale platform should I scrape?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The three biggest contenders ‚Äî Made-in-China.com, DHgate.com, and Yiwugo.com ‚Äî each serve different markets and offer different data. Let's break down what matters for developers and data teams.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2&gt;


Platform Overview
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


Made-in-China.com
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Focus&lt;/strong&gt;: B2B manufacturing and industrial products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Strength&lt;/strong&gt;: Heavy machinery, raw materials, industrial components&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Buyer type&lt;/strong&gt;: Factory buyers, procurement teams, importers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Listing style&lt;/strong&gt;: Detailed product specs with MOQ (Minimum Order Quantity)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


DHgate.com
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Focus&lt;/strong&gt;: B2B2C cross-border e-commerce&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Strength&lt;/strong&gt;: Consumer electronics, fashion, accessories, dropshipping-friendly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Buyer type&lt;/strong&gt;: Dropshippers, small retailers, individual buyers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Listing style&lt;/strong&gt;: Retail-style with single-piece ordering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


Yiwugo.com
&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Focus&lt;/strong&gt;: Yiwu International Trade City (world's largest small commodities market)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Strength&lt;/strong&gt;: Small commodities, daily necessities, gifts, toys, accessories&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Buyer type&lt;/strong&gt;: Wholesale buyers, market traders, small business owners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Listing style&lt;/strong&gt;: Market booth-based with physical location data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

