&lt;h2&gt;


Technical Scraping Comparison
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;


Made-in-China.com
&lt;/h3&gt;



&lt;div class="highlight js-code-highlight"&gt;
&lt;pre class="highlight plaintext"&gt;&lt;code&gt;Architecture: Server-side rendered HTML
Anti-bot: Cloudflare + rate limiting
Rendering: No JS required for basic data
Challenge: IP-based rate limiting, occasional CAPTCHAs
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;



&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pros:&lt;/strong&gt; Clean HTucture, no JS rendering needed, detailed structured specs.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Cons:&lt;/strong&gt; Aggressive rate limiting, some data requires login, Cloudflare protection.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;


DHgate.com
&lt;/h3&gt;


&lt;div class="highlight js-code-highlight"&gt;
&lt;pre class="highlight plaintext"&gt;&lt;code&gt;Architecture: Server-side rendered + dynamic loading
Anti-bot: Cloudflare + behavioral analysis
Rendering: Some sections need JS
Challenge: Price data sometimes loaded dynamically
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pros:&lt;/strong&gt; Huge catalog (30M+), rich data per product (reviews, ratings, order count).&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Cons:&lt;/strong&gt; More aggressive anti-bot, some data requires JS rendering.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;


Yiwugo.com
&lt;/h3&gt;


&lt;div class="highlight js-code-highlight"&gt;
&lt;pre class="highlight plaintext"&gt;&lt;code&gt;Architecture: Traditional server-rendered pages
Anti-bot: Basic rate limiting
Rendering: No JS required
Challenge: Chinese-language interface
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pros:&lt;/strong&gt; Simplest to scrape, unique booth location data, true wholesale pricing.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Cons:&lt;/strong&gt; Smaller catalog, primarily Chinese language.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;


Which Platform Should You Scrape?
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Choose Made-in-China.com if:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You need industrial/manufacturing product data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your users are B2B procurement teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You need detailed product specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Choose DHgate if:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You're building dropshipping or retail arbitrage tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You need consumer product data with reviews&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your users buy in small quantities (1-100 pieces)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Choose Yiwugo if:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You're focused on small commodities and daily goods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You need true wholesale pricing (not retail markup)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Physical market data (booth numbers) matters&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
